# Schuhvana

Schuhvana is an online marketplace for fashionable sports shoes, built using Vue.js.

## Project setup

```bash
npm install
```

Compiles and hot-reloads for development

```bash
npm run build
```

Lints and fixes files
```bash
npm run lint
```

Features

	•	Product listing with filters
	•	Shopping cart and checkout
	•	User login and registration
	•	Order history
	•	Search functionality

Technologies Used

	•	Vue 3
	•	Vuex (State management)
	•	Vue Router (Routing)
	•	Axios (API calls)

Folder Structure

	•	src/components: Reusable Vue components
	•	src/views: Application pages (Home, Product, Cart, Checkout, etc.)
	•	src/store: Vuex store for state management
	•	src/utils: Utility functions (API calls, validators, etc.)

Configuration

Make sure to add your API URL in a .env file:

```bash
VUE_APP_API_URL=https://api.example.com
```